        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Most of the features are now working and I'm thinking about an actual release.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Most of the features are now working and I'm thinking about an actual release.</p><p>There are still some design choices that I'd like to review before I commit to a major version release,
but I think I'm almost there.</p><p>Rob</p>]]></content>
